System design
This system use two operating platforms:
A. One UPBOARD with Ubuntu 18.04 distrubution
B. One UPBOARD with Yocto Linux distribution
The two boards will be connected using a local network connection and transfer data from one to each other.
C. The boards will have an android application that will control the interaction and movement of the robot.
D. The MCU will control the main board and reset the platform when it is stucked.Ft
